### Successful Invite and Duplicate Invite - (POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/businesses/<businessId>/members, Authorization: Bearer <owner-access-token>, email = use B's)

POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/businesses/6a463756eed8cb5e2897566f/members
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI2YTQ2MzRhYjczNGMyM2I3MTkwMjY2ODEiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImRlc2lnbnNvbHV0aW9uczE2MjlAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzgyOTg3MjE5LCJleHAiOjE3ODI5ODgxMTksImF1ZCI6InRhc3NpYXFjYS1jbGllbnQiLCJpc3MiOiJ0YXNzaWFxY2EifQ.ojujf1tHly7u3wostWylLjAYob-y8ID61wwEOn7HVZg
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "rembo1234@gmail.com",
    "roleId": "6a451ec4b20eb8419e8a8be6"
}

